Package registry.element

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    NumberDataElement
    Interface for number-type elements (INT, LONG, SHORT etc.)
    StringDataElement
    Interface for string type elements
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AStrLDataElement
    ASCII String Element - fixed length
    AStrZDataElement
    ASCII String Element - zero terminated
    BinDataElement
    Binary data element
    DataElement
    Defines an element of specified type at specified offset into RegistryBuffer This is the base (abstract) class Concrete element types will descend from here
    DataElementArray
    Wraps an array of DataElement
    DataElementCollection  
    DataElementMap
    Implements a map of DataElement using enums This allows elements to be selected by either index or enum
    FiletimeDataElement
    Windows FILETIME data element
    FormatElement
    Helper functions to format elements as hex
    IntDataElement
    INTEGER data element
    LongDataElement
    LONG data element
    NkFlagsDataElement
    NK cell flags data element
    ShortDataElement
    SHORT data element
    UStrLDataElement
    UNICODE String - fixed length
    UStrZDataElement
    UNICODE String - zero terminated
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ElementType
    Enum of element data types
